    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mad World Survivors is a fast-paced rogue-lite shooter where you battle relentless hordes of monsters in a world consumed by chaos. Players must survive intense combat where every decision could be their last. If you enjoy quick action, unique character abilities, and ever-changing battle conditions, this game is for you!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What to expect:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Non-stop action with countless enemies and powerful abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedurally generated runs: every attempt is unique, adding endless replayability.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Progression system: choose your hero and upgrade abilities. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Affordable price and regular updates crafted with community care.</p></li></ul>",
